creator: Sense - immaterial Reality srl
descriptionHtml:
SenseFabric is an application that simulates all properties of fabrics as texture, color, light behaviour, weight.
Using Sense technology users can “touch” the sample, appreciate its physical behaviour interacting with this moving the smartphone, can zoom in the texture to see all details and can have complete catalogue available at any time.
With SenseFabric companies can produce a much smaller number of physical samples keeping intact the possibility of the customer to view the entire color catalog offered by them, with a significant saving of time and money.
descriptionShort: SenseFabric simulates all properties of fabrics.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- improved fabric behavior through even more realistic simulation than ever
- possibility to experience fabric thickness
- light temperature set up
- opportunity to save preferable samples to favorite folder
- possibility to compare colors and textures of chosen samples
- possibility to create private areas to share “confidential” fabrics with the customer
- possibility to see fabrics on a mannequin in 3D and immaterial reality
